Body (
Fig. 1F
) oval, shining, sparsely covered with fulvous hairs. Coloration of head, pronotum and elytra black with bluish luster; antennae yellow, with apical 8 or 9 segments black; elytra with a wide yellow fascia just before the middle; tibiae, trochanters, apex of coxae, fore femora; apical portion of middle femora yellow.

